<div>
<em>Published in final edited form as: </em>J Biomed Inform. 2015 Jul 15;57:88–99. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jbi.2015.06.023" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1016/j.jbi.2015.06.023</a>
</div>
<nav id="journal_context_menu" hidden="hidden"><ul class="menu-list font-family-ui" role="menu">
<li role="presentation"><a href='https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/search/?term="J%20Biomed%20Inform"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem">Search in PMC</a></li>
