<p id="P63">Detailed description of individual WHO items is available at <a href="http://www.who.int/ictrp/network/trds/en" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://www.who.int/ictrp/network/trds/en</a>.</p>
